snippet.title: Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2 - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Cloudy Super Mario Bros. U 2, the New Super Mario Bros. U for Wii U mod I have been working on for over 4 years, has finally been released!
Download: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/12pAcqt93Jw2dAm2NU0Mkf5YjOaU6Ck2d

This mod features:
- Over 40 intricately designed levels
- A soundtrack featuring both original and familiar tunes
- Dozens of new tilesets and other visually overhauled level elements

If you have any questions about the mod or would like to learn more about modding New Super Mario Bros. Wii and / or New Super Mario Bros. U, be sure to join the Evolution Discord Server: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ

Check out the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct which originally hosted the premiere of this trailer: https://youtu.be/dvAH9bEEuPk
